title: Pixel 3a Wrong Model Number?
content:
I have a Pixel 3a 
North American Variant
MFR # GA00655-US
The model number on the box is G020G.
The model number under settings >About phone>regulatory labels is G020C.

According to the Safety & regulatory manual (Pixel 3a & Pixel 3a XL 2019)
Models:
Pixel 3a:       G020E, G020F, G020G, G020H 
Pixel 3a XL:  G020A, G020B, G020C, G020D
https://support.google.com/pixelphone/answer/9224138?hl=en

Was my Pixel 3a built incorrectly ?

Thanks.
